snippet.title: Faction Focus: Disciples Of Tzeentch | Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin
snippet.description:
Pre-order now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1844380/Warhammer_Age_of_Sigmar_Realms_of_Ruin/

Discover the schemes from masters of sorcerous rites and manipulation, the Disciples of Tzeentch, in the fourth and final Faction Focus video series. Embody Tzeentch and the mastery of change with powerful customisation tools within your grasp.

Pre-order the Deluxe and Ultimate Edition for up to 3 days Early Unlock.

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/RealmsofRuin

Follow us on:

Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/frontier
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RealmsOfRuin
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlayRealmsOfRuin
Instagram: https://instagram.com/RealmsOfRuin
